Chordate:



He kissed Feline's cheek.  "Alright." he said.  He looked to Gigatron.  
"Yeah, there are plenty of free quarters." he was getting a tad bit annoyed.  
He wanted to go outside already.  There's always something when he wants to 
do something.'

He let out an annoyed sigh as Feline spoke to him about needing to go to a 
conference room.  "Slag.  Come on, I'll show you." Chordate kissed her cheek 
again, walking down a corridor.
